    "answer": "## 跨域（Cross-Origin）\n\n### 同源策略（Same-Origin Policy）\n浏览器的安全机制，限制不同源之间的资源访问。\n\n**同源条件**：协议、域名、端口三者完全相同\n```\nhttps://a.com:443/path\n协议: https\n域名: a.com\n端口: 443\n```\n\n**跨域示例**\n```\nhttps://a.com → http://a.com  （协议不同）\nhttps://a.com → https://b.com （域名不同）\nhttps://a.com → https://a.com:8080 （端口不同）\nhttps://a.com → https://sub.a.com  （子域名不同）\n```\n\n### 解决方案\n\n**1. CORS（推荐，后端配置）**\n```js\n// 服务器设置响应头\nAccess-Control-Allow-Origin: https://frontend.com\nAccess-Control-Allow-Methods: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE\nAccess-Control-Allow-Headers: Content-Type, Authorization\nAccess-Control-Allow-Credentials: true\n```\n\n**2. 开发环境代理（Vite）**\n```js\n// vite.config.js\nexport default {\n  server: {\n    proxy: {\n      '/api': {\n        target: 'http://localhost:3000',\n        changeOrigin: true,\n        rewrite: (path) => path.replace(/^\\/api/, '')\n      }\n    }\n  }\n};\n```\n\n**3. Nginx 反向代理**\n```nginx\nlocation /api/ {\n  proxy_pass http://backend:3000/;\n  proxy_set_header Host $host;\n}\n```\n\n**4. JSONP（只支持 GET，已过时）**\n```js\nfunction jsonp(url, callback) {\n  const fn = 'jsonp_' + Date.now();\n  window[fn] = callback;\n  const script = document.createElement('script');\n  script.src = `${url}?callback=${fn}`;\n  document.head.appendChild(script);\n}\n```",
